<div class="accordion-item parbase section">
        <div id="accordion-142825-divestment-schedule" class="accordion-item-wrapper" data-alias="divestment-schedule">
            <a href="faqs#divestment-schedule" class="accordion-item-link">
                <h3 class="accordion-item-header">淡马锡有资产脱售时间表吗？</h3>
                
                <span class="accordion-item-icon"> </span>
            </a>
            <div class="accordion-item-content-wrapper">
                <div class="accordion-item-content-inner">
<div class="parsys"><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="default"><p>淡马锡并没有脱售资产的时间表。</p>
<p>淡马锡是一家投资公司，不时重塑其投资组合。所有投资、脱售或继续持有投资是根据淡马锡的内涵价值测试来决定。</p>
</div>


