<div class="accordion-item parbase section">
        <div id="accordion-142825-does-shareholder-inject-capital-into-temasek" class="accordion-item-wrapper" data-alias="does-shareholder-inject-capital-into-temasek">
            <a href="faqs#does-shareholder-inject-capital-into-temasek" class="accordion-item-link">
                <h3 class="accordion-item-header">股东是否向淡马锡注资？</h3>
                
                <span class="accordion-item-icon"> </span>
            </a>
            <div class="accordion-item-content-wrapper">
                <div class="accordion-item-content-inner">
<div class="parsys"><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="default"><p>我们的股东可能通过对淡马锡新的股份投资，为淡马锡注资。对淡马锡股份的投资反映在淡马锡的经审计的财务报表中，是公开信息。对淡马锡股份的所有投资是作为股东整体资产配置的一部分。</p>
</div>


</div>

</div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
