<div class="accordion-item parbase section">
        <div id="accordion-142825-does-temasek-guarantee-to-portfolio-companies-debts" class="accordion-item-wrapper" data-alias="does-temasek-guarantee-to-portfolio-companies-debts">
            <a href="faqs#does-temasek-guarantee-to-portfolio-companies-debts" class="accordion-item-link">
                <h3 class="accordion-item-header">淡马锡是否为其投资组合公司的债务提供担保?</h3>
                
                <span class="accordion-item-icon"> </span>
            </a>
            <div class="accordion-item-content-wrapper">
                <div class="accordion-item-content-inner">
<div class="parsys"><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="default"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 115.0%;">按照公司政策，淡马锡不为所投公司的债务提供任何财务担保。</p>
</div>


</div>

</div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</div>

</div>

    </div>

    <script src="https://localhost:8087/etc.clientlibs/temasek-commons/components/functional/accordion/clientlibs.min.js"></script>

</div>

</div>

